AllProduct.name: Mercedes AMG Model 2020
AllProduct.productDescription: While just about everything Mercedes Benz makes gets a hotter AMG version, that might be coming to a close as Mercedes Benz looks to eliminate up to 75 percent of their AMG line up in order to meet rising fleet emission standards according to reports. European standards and some states require an average CO2 emission across the range of their vehicles while the AMG models with their focus on large high output engines drag down Mercedes Benz average.
